      :
      <b>
       scty, rmgnd: hw t mk t rlty
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Thr ws  lt f pstv rctn t my lst pst:
       <a href="http://mnmlist.com/reimagined/">
        scty, rmgnd
       </a>
       … nd t ws ncrgng, t sy th lst. Lts f ppl wnt t lv n  wrld tht’s cr-fr, dgtl (xcpt fr bks, whch mny ppl dn’t wnt t gv p), nschld, lcvr, nn-cnsmrst, wth lts f fr tm nstd f wg slvry.
      </p>
      <p>
       Hr’s th thng: y cn lrdy hv t, rght nw.
      </p>
      <p>
       S ftn w frgt tht th thngs tht cnstrn s … thy’r n r hds. Thy dn’t xst n th rl wrld, xcpt whr w blv thy xst. Mny, fr xmpl … w lrdy lv n  mnylss wrld, s mny nly xsts n r hds. Sr, thr’s th physcl ppr mny r gld cns, bt ths hv n vl xcpt th vl w blv thy hv, nd r blty t by thngs wth mny, r nd t d wrk fr mny, r strss vr nt hvng mny r wng mny … t nly xsts n r hds. Th wrld rnd s, f w sddnly stppd blvng n mny, wld b mnylss.
      </p>
      <p>
       Gvrnmnts r th sm. Th
       <span class="caps">
        U.S.
       </span>
       Dclrtn f Indpndnc stts tht “Gvrnmnts r nstttd mng Mn, drvng thr jst pwrs frm th cnsnt f th gvrnd” … bt ctlly, thy xst nly n th mnds f th gvrnd, nd nly hv pwr s lng s th gvrnd llw thm t hv pwr. Th sm ppls t ny systm: schls, wrk, bnks, nd s n — thy xst n r mnds.
      </p>
      <p>
       And s, t lv n  wrld rmgnd, w nly nd t s r mgntns. W hv tht pwr lrdy.
       <span id="more-617">
       </span>
      </p>
      <p>
       Wnt t lv n  cr-fr wrld? Stp sng  cr. Nw th wrld y lv n bcms n n whch y wlk, bk, nd s mss trnst. Othrs mght nt fllw, bt tht’s thr chc. If y wnt t lv whr thr rn’t ny crs,
       <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_carfree_places">
        thr xst sch plcs
       </a>
       nd y cn mv t n f ths plcs, f tht’s mprtnt t y. Bt lrdy, y cn lv n  cr-fr wrld.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wnt t lv n  wrld whr yr fd sn’t shppd thsnds f mls nd grwn nsstnbly by grbsnss? Strt  grdn. Y cn jst strt wth n plnt, nd thn nthr, ntl y hv ngh t t vntlly. Or strt
       <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Community_gardening">
        cmmnty grdn
       </a>
       , r s frmr’s mrkts, r jn (r strt)
       <a href="http://www.localharvest.org/csa/">
        <span class="caps">
         CSA
        </span>
       </a>
       .
      </p>
      <p>
       Wnt t lv n n nschld wrld? Unschl yr kds. It’s nt hrd, nd tks zr rsrcs — lthgh th Intrnt nd th lbrry r grt f y cn gt thm, nd th wrld rnd s s n nlmtd rsrc fr dctn.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wnt t lv n  nn-cnsmrst wrld? Stp byng thngs. Mk thngs lst, rs thngs nd mv t rsbl thngs (sch s clth npkns nd glss cntnrs), fx thngs whn thy brk, trd, jn
       <a href="http://freecycle.org">
        Frcycl
       </a>
       . Stp wtchng ds (whch mght mn y stp wtchng TV r rdng d-spprtd mgzns nd nwspprs).
      </p>
      <p>
       Wnt t lv n  pprlss wrld? Stp byng nd sng ppr. Wnt t wrk frm hm r nr yr hm? Strt  bsnss whr y cn d tht nw (t csts lmst nthng), r wrk wth yr bss t tlcmmt.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wnt hppnss? Evrythng y nd s lrdy hr, n th wrld rnd y: btfl ppl, grgs ntr, th lgs y nd t wlk mng ths thngs, nd th ys, rs nd mth y nd t pprct thm.
      </p>
      <p>
       I cknwldg tht w wn’t stp glbl wrmng wth jst r wn ctns, bt t th lst, w’v stppd prtcptng n th dstrctn f r plnt … nd t bst, w nspr thrs by shwng thm t’s pssbl.
      </p>
      <p>
       I rlz ths thngs wld b bttr wth lrgr nmbrs, s fnd  frnd r fmly mmbr wllng t jn y, nd y hv  prtnr. Thn  thrd, nd  frth, nd nw y hv  clb. Gt  ffth, nd y hv  mvmnt. And thn y hv sm rl mgc.
      </p>
      <p>
       Bt th mgc, my frnds, cn strt tdy.
      </p>
